SUMMARY:Tambo Salsa/Bachata Social
DESCRIPTION:One of your favorites places to dance salsa is Dante Alighieri Hall in Cambridge. All the music and friendly environment you like and want. Bring your dance shoes and get ready to dance the night away meeting new friends and having fun. \n– 8:45pm Salsa lesson\n– 9:30pm – 1am Music\n– Performances (on certain events)\n– Cover $20 Lesson + Party\, $15 Party only \nFree parking and full bar.\nPlease RSVP the event and INVITE YOUR friends\n$5 discount for students with ID
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/tambo-salsa-bachata-social/2026-05-08/
LOCATION:Dante Alighieri Society of Massachusetts\, 41 Hampshire Street\, Cambridge\, MA 02139\, Cambridge\, MA\, 02139\, United States
CATEGORIES:Boston
END:VEVENT
